Package: libnet-ldapapi-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libldap2
Description:  A C API interface to LDAP servers
 The Net-LDAPapi perl module use the OpenLDAP C API or Mozilla C SDK
 to provide an fast and robust interface to LDAP servers.
